Target: OntoService is designed to represent the terms, conditions, and obligations associated with service delivery as well as the execution details.

Comment: Legally enforceable duty and payment terms for the associated service stated in a service agreement.
Label: Service payment obligation

Comment: A service that acts as a point of contact for communication, support, or assistance.
Label: Contact service

Comment: A quantifiable measure to evaluate and track the performance, quality, or efficiency of a service against predefined standards and expectations. These metrics include response time, weight, and customer satisfaction, among others.
Label: Service metric

Comment: The quantifiable weight measured in tons when the service is performed.
Label: Service tonnage

Comment: The maximum allowable value for the metric defined in the service agreement.
Label: Service metric cap

Comment: The phase in the lifecycle of a contract to create a new contract.
Label: Creation stage

Comment: The phase in the lifecycle of a contract where the services agreed should be executed.
Label: Service execution stage

Comment: The phase in the lifecycle of a contract where the contract has ended.
Label: Expiration stage

Comment: An event to draft and create a new contract during the creation lifecycle stage of a contract.
Label: Contract creation

Comment: An event to approve the contract during the creation lifecycle stage of a contract.
Label: Contract approval

Comment: An event ending the contract as all contractual obligations have been performed.
Label: Contract discharge

Comment: An event rendering the contract null, void, and no longer legally binding as one contractual party is a victim of a vitiating factor during the expiration lifecycle stage of a contract.
Label: Contract rescission

Comment: An event ending the contract before all contractual obligations have been performed. Typically the contract may have been concluded earlier with the agreement of all parties involved.
Label: Contract termination

Comment: A base charge for the service agreed in the contract.
Label: Base charge

Comment: A charge that depends on the outcome of a service after execution, agreed upon in the contract.
Label: Variable charge

Comment: The final price that the client should pay for the service, inclusive of taxes.
Label: Total price

Comment: Gross service price for all service charges, excluding taxes.
Label: Gross price

Comment: A tax rate incurred upon the service.
Label: Tax

Comment: The rates that is dependent on the outcome of a service after execution, agreed upon in the contract.
Label: Variable rate

Comment: The rates that is dependent on the outcome of a service after execution, agreed upon in the contract. Specifically, this rate will be in effect once the service exceeds the cap specified.
Label: Excess variable rate

Comment: A relationship describing the contact point for another service.
Label: serves as contact for

Comment: A relationship that links the obligations made when providing or engaging with the associated service.
Label: obliged to

Comment: A relationship describing a legally enforceable base charge for each service.
Label: has base charge

Comment: A relationship describing a legally enforceable variable rate for a service based on certain parameters.
Label: has variable rate

Comment: A relationship defining the numerator of a monetary rate, which should be amount of money.
Label: has numerator

Comment: A relationship defining the denominator of a monetary rate, which depends on the service metric.
Label: has denominator

Comment: A relationship describing the service metric that the variable rate is based on.
Label: depends on

Comment: A relationship describing the service metric that the variable rate is based on.
Label: depends on

Comment: A relationship defining the quantity of a service metric.
Label: has quantity

Comment: A relationship defining the quantity of a service metric.
Label: has quantity

Comment: A relationship describing the service location, typically a point, within the building or site.
Label: has service location

Comment: A relationship assigning a transport vehicle to a service event.
Label: assign transport

Comment: A relationship describing the final charge of a service event.
Label: charges

Comment: A relationship describing the time window for the regular schedule with a corresponding start and end time.
Label: has time slot
